imes we now live in he is proud to be a part of lively arts and working with the usher team and helping to keep live theater alive while on campus he also assists other departments with their events such as the roundtable the dalai lama's visit bill walsh memorial service baccalaureate commencement the aurora forum series and many others being a part of the stanford community keeps his spirits high and helps to look forward to the challenges the future might bring email bstarr stanford edu phone 650 725 1962 press info faq contact us privacy & legal site developed by mark hurty stanford lively arts tickets 650 725 arts email ticketorders stanford edu admin office 650 723 2551 email livelyarts stanford edu stanford university 425 santa teresa street mc 2250 stanford ca 94305 copyright 2000 2012 stanford lively arts like us on facebook watch us on vimeo follow us on twitter
